summary: Warning: The Surgeon General Has Determined that Cigrere Smoking ls Dangerous to Your Health. The U.S. Department of Health and Human Services has determined that smoking is dangerous to your health. Smoking is linked to high blood pressure, heart disease, lung cancer, and other conditions.
